attributes.Long form description: The student begins by changing the GoPro battery when the student finishes the student waits for new instructions and the instructor tells him to change the SD card and then turn on and off the GoPro. After turning off the GoPro the instructor tells the student to mount up the GoPro to the strap and to the handheld grip and then dismount it and place the GoPro on the table.

attributes.Transcription: Now please change the battery of the GoPro.

attributes.Action sentence: The student removes the old battery.

attributes.Action Correctness: Wrong Action, corrected by instructor verbally
attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student pulls the battery door in the wrong way.

attributes.Transcription: You will need to pull that down and then open it up to the side.

attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student pulls the battery door incorrectly.
The student can't find the right way to open the battery door.

attributes.Action sentence: The student inserts the new battery.

attributes.Transcription: Now please change the micro SD card of the GoPro.

attributes.Action sentence: The student exchanges the micro SD card of the gopro.

attributes.Action Correctness: Wrong Action, corrected by instructor verbally
attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student can't find the micro sd slot.

attributes.Transcription: The micro SD card is at the same place as the battery.
Now please turn on the GoPro.

attributes.Action sentence: The student turns on the GoPro.

attributes.Transcription: Now please turn off the GoPro again.

attributes.Action sentence: The student turns off the GoPro.
The student places the strap on the GoPro.

attributes.Action Correctness: Wrong Action, corrected by instructor verbally
attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student doesn't know what to do.

attributes.Transcription: You need to pull out the two holes from the GoPro.
Now please change from the straps to the handheld grip.

attributes.Action sentence: The student exchanges the strap for the handheld grip

attributes.Transcription: Now please remove the handheld grip.

attributes.Action sentence: The student removes the GoPro from the handheld grip.

attributes.Transcription: You can stop the recording now.
